ImportOntologyFileJob, ImportOntologyURLJob
public abstract class ImportOntologyJob
extends org.eclipse.core.runtime.jobs.Job
implements org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLOntologyLoaderListener

Abstract class for importing ontologies as a background task visible to the user. Implementations must provide loadOntology(IProgressMonitor) method and append occurred exceptions via the appendException(Throwable) method.
